 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062d\u064f\u0630\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15284,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/22\/barakah-sharing-food\/","url_meta":{"origin":5756,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Meals: Blessings in sharing food with others","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe food of one person is enough for two, the food of two is enough for four, and the food of four is enough for eight.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2059 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim Imam\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25583,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/10\/wudu-nawm-junub\/","url_meta":{"origin":5756,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Perform ablution if sleeping with major impurity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 10, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: If the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, intended to sleep while in a state of major ritual impurity, he would perform ablution before he slept. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 282, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 305 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25464,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/29\/raising-hands-in-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":5756,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Description of raising the hands in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 29, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would raise his hands parallel to his shoulders when he entered into prayer, and when he exalted Allah for bowing. When he raised his head from bowing, he would likewise raise his hands and say, \u201cAllah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13557,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/13\/tahiyyat-al-masjid\/","url_meta":{"origin":5756,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Greet mosque with Tahiyyatul Masjid prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 13, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Qatadah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you enters the mosque, let him pray two cycles before he sits down.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 444, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 714 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33923,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/01\/13\/istighfar-after-salah\/","url_meta":{"origin":5756,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Seeking forgiveness, supplicating after prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 13, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Thawban reported: When the Messenger of Allah peace and blessings be upon him, finished his prayer, he would seek forgiveness from Allah three times and he would say, \u201cO Allah, You are peace and from You is peace. Blessed are You, Majestic and Generous.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 591 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5756","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"e